Reviews.Title: Great Value
Reviews.Author: Extremely Satisfied with Pink Moose Company
Reviews.Content: The price for these power cable extension wires is a great value - I could not find this value anywhere locally and after installing they worked just as well as the more expensive one I bought and installed. Save money - if you need a BNC video cable buy this.

Reviews.Title: excellent product
Reviews.Author: anthony smith
Reviews.Content: I can't say enough about this product.  I will definitely buy more of these  for all of my camera jobs.

Reviews.Title: Junk
Reviews.Author: AmazonRick
Reviews.Content: This item is a nicely packaged, nice looking set of very poor quality cables.  If your are looking for RG59 or RG6-type cables this product is not for you.  If you want to save $$ and take a chance -- got for it!I requested a return but when the return authorization came w/o a pre-paid label, I decided to cut my losses and just throw them in the trash.

Reviews.Title: No.1
Reviews.Author: gman
Reviews.Content: Best service and product I have ever had. In addition, this site save people money and time they get your order right the first time

Reviews.Title: video camera cables
Reviews.Author: Pete Duro
Reviews.Content: What can i say about a bunch of cables? They seem to be of good quality. they came with an adapter which was nice IF i needed. They work really well with my lorex 16 camera setups
